T*
(|---|---|) Tj
T*
(| is_bot | Required binary prediction in submission.tsv; 1 means selected as likely bot) Tj
T*
(traffic. |) Tj
T*
(| heuristic_score | Score from transparent rules such as repetition, timing, and burst) Tj
T*
(checks. |) Tj
T*
